{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7fd7b241a","title":"“胡风不是反革命”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1c0fd787f2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"f7fd7b241a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3d25ad450b","name":"陈汉良"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"995556a2cb","name":"王兰锟"},{"id":"a6507c0f56","name":"解天立"},{"id":"ca8e731aaa","name":"边兆祥"},{"id":"d05847b78e","name":"孙增垣"},{"id":"ec445d94b0","name":"蔡荣荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"41ec9c405b","type":"title","text":"“胡风不是反革命”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"52df8be5d9","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院孙增垣王兰锟陈汉良边兆祥蔡荣荣解天立","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"d12fde8f5a","type":"appellation","text":"孙增垣说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"500ba5d239","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风的三十万字意见书要是在『百家争鸣』的今天提出来，不但不能被当作反革命，反而会受到广大人民群众的拥护和喜闻乐见呢！胡风的这种作法处是『舍身求法』『为民请命』，大有『史官』的作法，如方孝儒一样诛十族在所不惜。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"93693a3c50","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风不是反革命分子。」","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"ff01105024","type":"appellation","text":"王兰锟说：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"1424d66dfd","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风是反革命值得怀疑。」","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"fd223600bf","type":"appellation","text":"陈汉良说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"864187db00","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风是反革命值得怀疑，据三批材料不能证明，罪状为什么不公布。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"803a89610c","type":"appellation","text":"边兆祥说：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"1899699e5c","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风是反革命值得怀疑。」","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"2ede14ee94","type":"appellation","text":"蔡荣荣说：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"55bdb64493","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风是反革命理由不充足，不能单凭信件就断定人家是反革命，即使是反革命，为何逮捕两年多不审判？」","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"65ecce73a5","type":"appellation","text":"解天立说：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"},{"id":"7dd534f04b","type":"appellation","text":"「胡风只是思想问题，不是反革命，两年多都不公布审判结果就是证明，胡风与章伯钧比起来差得多了，顶多是个右派。胡风的信件，只表示思想问题，党借此案件向一些有思想问题和有历史问题的人进行群众性的斗争，因为以前一直没有斗争的机会。」","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a"}],"page":{"id":"2a6e3233d1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7fd7b241a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}